4
00:00:10,650 --> 00:00:12,255
u oddiy matnda bo‘ladi.

5
00:00:12,255 --> 00:00:14,125
Shunday qilib, bu to‘g‘ri.

6
00:00:14,125 --> 00:00:18,329
Ikkinchisi - bu sizning telefoningizdagi musiqa.

7
00:00:18,329 --> 00:00:23,745
Keling, musiqa faylini olib, uni matn muharririda ochsak nima bo‘lishini ko‘rib chiqaylik.

8
00:00:23,745 --> 00:00:27,914
Menda Betxoven to‘qqizinchi simfonik MP3 fayli bor.

9
00:00:27,914 --> 00:00:30,554
