10
00:00:30,554 --> 00:00:33,375
Voy, qandoq ahmoqlik,

11
00:00:33,375 --> 00:00:37,619
matn muharriri faylni matn sifatida ochishga urinmoqda, turli tartibsizliklarni keltirib chiqarmoqda,

12
00:00:37,619 --> 00:00:39,340
ammo unday emas.

13
00:00:39,340 --> 00:00:42,570
Matn muharriri mp3 fayl bilan nima qilishni bilmaydi.

14
00:00:42,570 --> 00:00:45,560
Musiqa fayllari aslida matn emasdirlar.

15
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:48,393
Uchinchisi Udacityning bosh sahifasi.

16
00:00:48,393 --> 00:00:50,969
Bosh sahifa HTMLdan iborat bolib,

17
00:00:50,969 --> 00:00:53,149
HTML esa matn shaklida yozilgan.

18
00:00:53,149 --> 00:00:55,225
Demak, bu ham to‘g‘ri.

19
00:00:55,225 --> 00:00:58,109
To‘rtinchisi - kuchukning fotosurati.

20
00:00:58,109 --> 00:01:00,204
Rasmlar matn emas.

21
00:01:00,204 --> 00:01:04,159
Brauzerlar rasmlarni qanday aks ettirishni bilishadi,

22
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:07,674
lekin siz uni matn muharririda ochishga harakat qilsangiz,

23
00:01:07,674 --> 00:01:09,204
siz mp3 musiqiy fayl kabi,

24
00:01:09,204 --> 00:01:11,829
katta tartibsizlikni ko‘rasiz.

25
00:01:11,829 --> 00:01:13,310
