29
00:01:20,484 --> 00:01:22,909
PDFni brauzeringizda yoki

30
00:01:22,909 --> 00:01:25,510
Adobe Acrobat kabi dasturda ko‘rsangiz,

31
00:01:25,510 --> 00:01:28,564
odatda so‘zlar, jumlalar va boshqalarni ko‘rishingiz mumkin.

32
00:01:28,564 --> 00:01:31,480
